      "description": "Reliable transportation at an affordable price, this vehicle is a practical choice for a budget-minded buyer seeking straightforward value. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who appreciates a no-frills car with plenty of life left for everyday use, errands, or a starter vehicle. A great opportunity to get on the road without stretching your budget.",
