    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable transportation without spending a fortune. Great as a starter car, a project, or just something to get you from A to B. Priced to sell and represented honestly\u2014come take a look and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Clean, straightforward driver with solid bones and plenty of life left for the next owner. Starts up, runs, and offers a surprisingly composed ride, with the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it a great budget commuter, weekend project, or first car for someone who likes to wrench. Not perfect cosmetically and it shows typical age-related wear, but the platform still feels dependable and has the kind of durability enthusiasts appreciate. If you want an affordable car with usable road manners and room to improve over time, this is a smart way in.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap way into a running car. Honest poor-condition driver. Starts, moves, gets the job done. Not pretty. Priced to sell fast at $8,400.",
